        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "briefDescription": "Through the \"Bank Tie-Up Scheme\", the Punjab Scheduled Castes Land Development & Finance Corporation (PSCLDFC) arranges loans through banks, and subsidy is provided by PSCLDFC. The permanent residents of Punjab belonging to Scheduled Castes and living Below Poverty Line are eligible.",
        "detailedDescription": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Through the \"Bank Tie-Up Scheme\", the Punjab Scheduled Castes Land Development & Finance Corporation (PSCLDFC) arranges loans through banks, and subsidy is provided by PSCLDFC. The permanent residents of Punjab belonging to Scheduled Castes and living Below Poverty Line are eligible under this scheme. This is a 100% State Sponsored Scheme, and only the permanent residents of the state of Punjab can apply for this scheme."
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
